ftly on climate change.<\/p>\n<p>Ealing Friends of the Earth have obtained a copy of the exhibition. It&#8217;s currently on display at West Ealing Library W13 9BT, and we plan to tour it around a number of locations within the borough.<\/p>\n<p>The exhibition has visited mosques, churches, universities, schools, community centres and events in several cities across the UK.<\/p>\n<p>More information about climate change from the UK Friends of the Earth is available <a href=\"https:\/\/friendsoftheearth.uk\/climate-change\">here<\/a>. We have some short videos about climate change <a href=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/short-videos-on-climate-energy-nature\/\">on this website<\/a>.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3d348fb elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3d348fb\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-60c6cc9\" data-id=\"60c6cc9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-caf075e elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"caf075e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"504\" src=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/LettersFromGlobalSouthView_trim-1024x504.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-7327\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/LettersFromGlobalSou